<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
{{> head title="About &mdash; Davis/Macleod" metaDescription="Meet the team behind Davis/Macleod. Learn about our investment philosophy, board seats, advisory board, and approach to backing entrepreneurs."}}
</head>
<body>

{{> nav activePage=activePage navLight=true}}

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h4 style="color: var(--color-secondary);">Who We Are</h4>
      <h1>About Davis/Macleod</h1>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <p>A family investment office with a singular focus: backing exceptional entrepreneurs who acquire and build enduring businesses.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story — Block 1: Intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-intro fade-up">
        <h4>Our Story</h4>
        <h2>Built by an Entrepreneur.<br>Backing the Next Generation of Owners.</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>Davis/Macleod was founded on a simple belief: exceptional entrepreneurs, given the right capital and support, can acquire and build enduring businesses in the lower middle market.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story — Block 2: Pull Quote -->
  <section class="story-quote fade-up">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-quote__inner">
        <div class="story-quote__line"></div>
        <p>Davis/Macleod exists to support the next generation of business owners with patient capital, practical experience, and true alignment.</p>
        <div class="story-quote__line"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story — Block 3: Narrative + Image -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col" style="align-items: start;">
        <div class="fade-up">
          <img src="images/about-story.jpg" alt="Davis/Macleod team" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 2px;">
        </div>
        <div class="fade-up delay-2">
          <p>The firm represents the partnership between two families. The Macleod side brings an operator&rsquo;s perspective, shaped by years of building and exiting businesses from the ground up. The Davis side brings a multi-decade history of investing family capital, primarily in real estate, with a long-term, patient approach to ownership.</p>
          <p class="mt-4">Together, that combination formed the foundation of Davis/Macleod: a platform designed to back entrepreneurial operators with aligned, long-duration capital.</p>
          <p class="mt-4">Unlike traditional funds, we invest family capital alongside a small group of like-minded partners. We are not constrained by short fund cycles or institutional mandates. That allows us to focus on long-term value creation, support entrepreneurs through the inevitable challenges of ownership, and make decisions with a multi-decade mindset.</p>
          <p class="mt-4">Our role is simple. We partner with talented, driven entrepreneurs who want to acquire and build enduring businesses. We provide capital, strategic guidance, and access to a network of operators and advisors, while giving management teams the autonomy to lead.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Members -->
  {{#each teamMembers}}
  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="fade-up">
          {{#if (hasLogo this.Image)}}
          <img src="{{logoUrl this.Image}}" alt="{{this.Name}}" style="width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 3/4; object-fit: cover;">
          {{else}}
          <div class="image-placeholder" style="aspect-ratio: 3/4;">{{this.Name}}</div>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="fade-up delay-2">
          <h4>{{this.Role}}</h4>
          <h2>{{this.Name}}</h2>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          {{{paragraphs this.Bio}}}
          {{#if ../boardSeats.length}}
          <h4 style="margin-top: 32px;">Current Board Seats</h4>
          <ul style="margin-top: 12px; padding-left: 0; list-style: none;">
            {{#each ../boardSeats}}
            <li style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 0.95rem;">{{#if this.Website}}<a href="{{this.Website}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-secondary);">{{this.Name}}</a>{{else}}{{this.Name}}{{/if}}</li>
            {{/each}}
          </ul>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  {{/each}}

  <!-- Advisory Board -->
  {{#if advisors.length}}
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header text-center fade-up">
        <h4>Our Network</h4>
        <h2>Advisory Board &amp; Collaborators</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>We are fortunate to work alongside a group of experienced operators, investors, and advisors who bring deep expertise across industries and functional areas.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="advisor-list">
        {{#each advisors}}
        <div class="advisor-row fade-up {{delayClass @index}}">
          <div class="advisor-row__image">
            {{#if (hasLogo this.Image)}}
            <img src="{{logoUrl this.Image}}" alt="{{this.Name}}">
            {{else}}
            <div class="advisor-row__placeholder">{{this.Name}}</div>
            {{/if}}
          </div>
          <div class="advisor-row__content">
            {{#if this.Role}}
            <div class="advisor-row__role">{{this.Role}}</div>
            {{/if}}
            <h3 class="advisor-row__name">{{this.Name}}</h3>
            {{#if this.Bio}}
            <p class="advisor-row__bio">{{this.Bio}}</p>
            {{/if}}
          </div>
        </div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  {{/if}}

  <!-- Our Values -->
  <section class="section section--dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header text-center fade-up">
        <h4>What Guides Us</h4>
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="philosophy-grid">
        <div class="philosophy-card fade-up delay-1">
          <div class="philosophy-card__number">01</div>
          <h3>Partnership First</h3>
          <p>We invest in people before businesses. The relationship between investor and operator is the foundation of everything we do. We earn trust through transparency and follow-through.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-card fade-up delay-2">
          <div class="philosophy-card__number">02</div>
          <h3>Permanent Mindset</h3>
          <p>We invest our own capital with the intent to hold indefinitely. This patience allows our CEOs to make decisions for the long term, not for the next quarterly report.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-card fade-up delay-3">
          <div class="philosophy-card__number">03</div>
          <h3>Community Impact</h3>
          <p>The businesses we invest in are community pillars &mdash; they employ local workers, serve local customers, and contribute to local economies. Stewardship of this responsibility matters to us.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Invest -->
  <section id="how-we-invest" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header fade-up">
        <h4>Our Strategies</h4>
        <h2>How We Invest</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>We deploy capital through three primary channels, each designed to back exceptional operators and build enduring businesses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="philosophy-grid" style="margin-top: 48px;">
        <div class="philosophy-card fade-up delay-1">
          <div class="philosophy-card__number">01</div>
          <h3>Search Funds</h3>
          <p>We back aspiring entrepreneurs who raise capital to search for, acquire, and operate a privately held company. Originated at Stanford GSB in the 1980s, the search fund model has become one of the most reliable paths to entrepreneurship through acquisition. We provide capital at both the search and acquisition stages, and serve as mentors, board members, and strategic partners throughout the journey.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-card fade-up delay-2">
          <div class="philosophy-card__number">02</div>
          <h3>Direct Acquisitions</h3>
          <p>We acquire businesses directly when we find the right combination of a strong company and a proven operator. In these transactions, we provide the capital and strategic support while partnering with a CEO to lead the business day-to-day. This approach allows us to move quickly on opportunities that fit our criteria.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-card fade-up delay-3">
          <div class="philosophy-card__number">03</div>
          <h3>Co-Investments</h3>
          <p>We invest alongside like-minded partners and operators in deals that align with our thesis. Co-investments allow us to participate in a broader range of opportunities while maintaining the selectivity and alignment that define our approach. We look for partners who share our long-term orientation and commitment to building enduring businesses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

{{> cta-banner heading="Let's Build Something Together" description="We are always looking for exceptional entrepreneurs to back. Whether you are exploring a search fund, pursuing an acquisition, or seeking a co-investment partner, we would love to hear from you." primaryLink="contact.html" primaryText="Start a Conversation" secondaryLink="portfolio.html" secondaryText="View Our Portfolio"}}

{{> footer}}

  <script src="js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>